<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1185.109154.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Serica species A-D S. breviantennalis Liu, Ahrens, Li & Su, sp. nov. (holotype) E-H S. breviantennalis (paratype) I-L S. allonanhua Liu, Ahrens, Li & Su, sp. nov. (paratype). A, E, I aedeagus, left side view C, G, K aedeagus, right side view B, F, J aedeagus, dorsal view D, H, L habitus (not to scale). Scale bars: 0.5 mm (A, B, C, E, F, G, I, J, K)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/943835" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1185.109154.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. The distribution map of Serica breviantennalis Liu, Ahrens, Li & Su, sp. nov., S. allonanhua Liu, Ahrens, Li & Su, sp. nov., S. fengensis Liu, Ahrens, Li & Su, sp. nov., including updated records of S. nanhua Ahrens, Fabrizi & Liu, 2022 and S. baishuitaiensis Ahrens, Fabrizi & Liu, 2022." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/943837" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

